            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Hd1e108">Rubrica 10</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De confidentia: credulitate et credulis atque incredulis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#P" n="27"/>De confidentia seu 
                credu<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="28"/>litate / et de credulis / et 
               <lb ed="#P" n="29"/>incredulis. capitulum. x. :-
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#P" n="30"/><ref>Isocrates in exortationibus. ca. ii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e129">Ex
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="31"/>pedire putes credendum esse 
               teme<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="32"/>rariis prout credendum est bonis seu 
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="33"/>probis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#P" n="34"/><ref>Aristoteles rethoricorum. libro. primo. ca. ii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="35"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e139">Modimus credimus magis et celerius</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e146">
               <lb ed="#P" n="36"/><ref>Ibidem libro. ii. ca. xvi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e148">Iuenes sunt 
               <lb ed="#P" n="37"/>facile credituri propterea quod nondum in 
               <lb ed="#P" n="38"/>multis decepti sunt. Iuuenes facile 
               <lb ed="#P" n="39"/>seducibiles sunt. sperant enim facile
               <lb ed="#P" n="40"/>Senes incredibiles sunt propter experientiam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e160">
               <lb ed="#P" n="41"/><ref>Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiastico. ca. xvii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="42"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e164">Non credas inimico tuo in eternum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#P" n="43"/><ref>Idem. ca. xviiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e172">Qui credit cito leuis 
               <lb ed="#P" n="44"/>est. corde / et minorabitur non omni verbo 
               <lb ed="#P" n="45"/>credas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e186">
               <lb ed="#P" n="46"/><ref>Tullius rethoricorum artis vereris libro
               <lb ed="#P" n="47"/>primo. ca. xii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e190">Summa amentia est eorum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="48"/>fidem / et spem habere / quorum perfidia de
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="49"/>ceptus sis multotiens.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#P" n="50"/><ref>Ibidem libro. iiii. ca. viiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e200">fidentia est 
               <lb ed="#P" n="51"/>per quam magnis / et honestis rebus
               <lb ed="#P" n="52"/>ipse animus in se fiducie cum spe collo
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="53"/>cauit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e210">
               <lb ed="#P" n="54"/><ref>Ouidius epistolarum epistola xvi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="55"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e214">Credulitas damno semper solet esse 
               <lb ed="#P" n="56"/>puellis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e221">
               <lb ed="#P" n="57"/><ref>Idem arte armandi libro. iii. et fi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="58"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e223">Nec cito credideris qui cito credere ledat
               <lb ed="#P" n="59"/>Exemplum nobis non leue prohorsus erit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#P" n="60"/><ref>Idem de tristibus. libro. iiii. epistola. iii.</ref>
               <lb ed="#P" n="61"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e235">Crede quod est vix. ac desine tuta 
               <lb ed="#P" n="62"/>vereri.
               <lb ed="#P" n="63"/>Deque fide certa sit tibi certa fides.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e243">
               <pb ed="#P" n="51-v"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="1"/><ref>Seneca declamationem libro. primo. ca. primo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e247">nemo 
               <lb ed="#P" n="2"/>facile credit. quo credito sit dolendum</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e253">
               <lb ed="#P" n="3"/><ref>Idem in proverbiis</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e255">utrumque vicium est
               <lb ed="#P" n="4"/>et omnibus credere et nulli.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e261">
               <lb ed="#P" n="5"/><ref>Iohannes epistola. primo. ca. iiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e265">nolite credere 
               <lb ed="#P" n="6"/>omni spiritui: sed probate spiritus si ex 
               <lb ed="#P" n="7"/>deo sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e273">
               <lb ed="#P" n="8"/><ref>Martialis cochus libro undique suscepto
               <lb ed="#P" n="9"/>ca. v.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e277">Omnibus et nulli credere te vi
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="10"/>tium est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e284">
               <lb ed="#P" n="11"/><ref>Vegetius de re militari. libro. iii. ca.
               <lb ed="#P" n="12"/>iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e288">Frequentius conuentiones pacisque 
               <lb ed="#P" n="13"/>simulatio credulis nocuere solent quam 
               <lb ed="#P" n="14"/>arma.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e296">
               <lb ed="#P" n="15"/><ref>Auctor libri de formula. honeste vite. ca. 
               <lb ed="#P" n="16"/>iiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e300">Rumoribus criminum et suspi
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="17"/>tionibus minime sis. credulus sed 
               <lb ed="#P" n="18"/>potius malignis qui per speciem simplicita
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="19"/>tis ad nocendum aliquibus surrepunt op
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="20"/>positi sumus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e312">
               <lb ed="#P" n="21"/><ref>Ambrosius de officiis libro. primo. ca. xxxi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="22"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e316">unusquisque bene volentis se magis quam 
               <lb ed="#P" n="23"/>sapientis credit consilio</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e324">
               <lb ed="#P" n="24"/><ref>Ibidem libro. ii. ca. viii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e326">potius nos 
               <lb ed="#P" n="25"/>iusto viro quam prudenti committimus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e332">
               <lb ed="#P" n="26"/><ref>Fulgentius mithologiarum libro. iii. et fi:
               <lb ed="#P" n="27"/>fabula. xv.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e336">Credulitas semper deceptionum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="28"/>mater est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e342">
               <lb ed="#P" n="29"/><ref>Cato. ca. primo.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="30"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e346">Nil temere credideris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e351">
               <lb ed="#P" n="31"/><ref>Idem. ca. iii.</ref>
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="32"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e353">Noli tu quedam referenti credere semper.
               <lb ed="#P" n="33"/>Exigua est tribuenda fides quia multi mul
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="34"/>ta loquntur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e363">
               <lb ed="#P" n="35"/><ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum libro. iiii. epistola. iiii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="36"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e367">illi credere debetis / quem vestris utilitati
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="37"/>bus arridere cognoscitis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e375">
               <lb ed="#P" n="38"/><ref>Versificator fabularum exopi fabula. ix.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="39"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e379">Non satis est tutum mellitis credere 
               <lb ed="#P" n="40"/>verbis. Ex hoc melle solet pestis ama
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="41"/>ra sequi</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e391">
               <lb ed="#P" n="42"/><ref>Idem fabula. xxv.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="43"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e395">Tempore non omni non omnibus omnia credas 
               <lb ed="#P" n="44"/>Qui misere credit creditur esse miser.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e401">
               <lb ed="#P" n="45"/><ref>Idem fabula. xxxi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="46"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e405">Qui me lesit iterum ledet si ledere posset
               <lb ed="#P" n="47"/>Expedit insido non interare fidem
               <lb ed="#P" n="48"/>Que dedit infidus mella venena puto.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e413">
               <lb ed="#P" n="49"/><ref>Baldo fabula. xi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="50"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e417">Nec confidatis secreta / nec his detegatis
               <lb ed="#P" n="51"/>Cum quibus egistis pugne discrimina testis</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e426">
               <lb ed="#P" n="52"/><ref>Idem fabula. xxvi.</ref>
               <lb ed="#P" n="53"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e428">Nulla fides hosti tibi sit suasio vilis.
               <lb ed="#P" n="54"/>Pro horsus / et hostilis sit tibi suasio uilis</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e436">
               <lb ed="#P" n="55"/><ref>Mattheus vindocinensis in poetria. parte.
               <lb ed="#P" n="56"/>primo. ca. xx.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e440">Credulitas sestina nocet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-d1e446">
               <lb ed="#P" n="57"/><ref>Prouerbium vulgare</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26532-Qd1e450">tuito credere non
               <lb ed="#P" n="58"/>e sapere.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
